@wp.kernel
def expr_auhcrr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v2 = wp.sin(0.55)
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.18) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.01)) * 0.94)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v2 + 0.74 + tmp + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
